ToolBox

public ToolBox(FileVersioner files,
               com.google.common.collect.ImmutableMap<java.lang.String,?> commonJsEnv,

               Logs logs,
               ArtifactListener<ToolSignature> listener,
               java.util.concurrent.ScheduledExecutorService execer)
        throws java.io.IOException
An initialized but inactive tool-box. Call start() to activate it.

Parameters:
files - versions any tool files that are under the client directory.
commonJsEnv - symbols available to tool files and plan files.
toolDirs - the set of directories to search for tools.
logs - receive messages about tool building progress.
listener - is updated when tool definitions are invalidated or validated.
execer - an executor which is used to schedule periodic maintenance tasks and which is used to update tool definitions.
Throws:
java.io.IOException
